&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced and highly analytical &lt;strong&gt;Omnichannel Operations Manager &lt;/strong&gt;to join the KHAITE team. This role will report to the Head of Global Logistics &amp;amp; Operations and will be based out of the NYC HQ offices. This role will lead and optimize operational execution across our Direct-to-Consumer business, including eCommerce, Retail Stores, Personal Shopping, and Fulfillment. This role will serve as a critical cross-functional partner, ensuring seamless customer experiences, operational excellence, inventory accuracy, and fulfillment performance across all channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a strategic problem solver with deep experience in retail, eCommerce, logistics, and omnichannel operations within a luxury or premium consumer brand. This individual will drive process improvements, establish best practices, manage key operational initiatives, and serve as the primary liaison between Retail, Customer Service, Distribution, Technology, Finance, and third-party logistics partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
