&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Visual Merchandising Intern &lt;/strong&gt;to join the KHAITE team for this Fall &#39;26 Semester. This role will report to the Director, Visual Merchandising and will be based out of the NYC HQ offices. This internship is unpaid and for college credit only.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ESSENTIAL DUTIES &amp;amp; RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1x72ri6&quot; data-start=&quot;70&quot; data-end=&quot;217&quot;&gt;Support the Visual Merchandising team with the execution of seasonal store updates, window installations, and in-store merchandising initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1h0g41d&quot; data-start=&quot;218&quot; data-end=&quot;353&quot;&gt;Assist with preparing visual merchandising guidelines, floor plans, product stories, and presentation materials for retail locations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;vh1l0f&quot; data-start=&quot;354&quot; data-end=&quot;477&quot;&gt;Help coordinate product pulls, styling requests, and inventory organization to support store launches and visual updates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1gs7ryy&quot; data-start=&quot;478&quot; data-end=&quot;597&quot;&gt;Conduct store visits and provide feedback on visual standards, product presentation, and merchandising opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;b4qd2c&quot; data-start=&quot;598&quot; data-end=&quot;733&quot;&gt;Support the preparation and execution of special events, activations, and retail experiences to ensure a cohesive brand presentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;zo9j0c&quot; data-start=&quot;734&quot; data-end=&quot;900&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;Research luxury retail trends, competitor environments, and visual storytelling techniques to provide insights and inspiration for future merchandising initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
